clouseau (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Daemon mode: watch loop detects Claude start/stop, logs per-session
  * Per-session timestamped log directories
  * Add tcplife tracing for connection duration and bytes transferred
  * Add -v flag for explicit verbose mode; auto-detect tty
  * Drop syscount tracing due to overhead
  * Remove sudo when running as root (systemd service support)

 -- Ian Brown <igb@hccp.org>  Sun, 29 Mar 2026 17:30:00 +0000

